---
// Hero section component extracted from index.astro
---

<section class="hero-section">
  <div class="hero-shadow-image-wrap">
    <img
      src="images/png-01_1png-01.avif"
      loading="lazy"
      alt="Shadow Image"
      class="hero-shadow-image"
    />
  </div>
  <div data-w-id="53ad0e5e-a245-1c48-bc1a-29cdbece4091" class="hero-wrapper">
    <div class="w-layout-blockcontainer container w-container">
      <div class="hero-title-wrap">
        <h1
          data-w-id="70578a58-bc50-ecc6-2def-5ecf216048ac"
          style="opacity:0"
          class="hero-title">
          Dr. Nicolas Scheffbuch
        </h1>
      </div>
      <div class="w-layout-grid grid-hero">
        <div
          data-w-id="f9007791-5903-0bd3-bade-c68157b5f755"
          style="opacity:0"
          class="hero-rating-wrap">
          <div class="hero-text-content">
            <span
              >Botox-Behandlungen in St. Gallen – persönlich, präzise, natürlich</span>
          </div>
          <a href="book-an-appointment.html" class="button-primary-2 w-button"
            >Jetzt Termin vereinbaren</a
          >
        </div>
        <div
          data-w-id="9f2cad1f-3109-1be8-4d28-bfb1f7722088"
          style="opacity:0"
          class="hero-image-wrap">
          <img
            src="images/f8c7d2df-794b-40bb-a799-9deb0a32c778.jpeg"
            loading="lazy"
            sizes="(max-width: 767px) 100vw, (max-width: 991px) 728px, 940px"
            srcset="images/f8c7d2df-794b-40bb-a799-9deb0a32c778-p-500.jpeg 500w, images/f8c7d2df-794b-40bb-a799-9deb0a32c778-p-800.jpeg 800w, images/f8c7d2df-794b-40bb-a799-9deb0a32c778-p-1080.jpeg 1080w, images/f8c7d2df-794b-40bb-a799-9deb0a32c778.jpeg 1170w"
            alt=""
          />
        </div>
        <div
          data-w-id="1b9e2bc5-2f44-5e83-ce50-0ec3d95cffd4"
          style="opacity:0"
          class="hero-content-wrap">
          <p>
            Minimalinvasive Ästhetik auf höchstem Niveau – direkt im
            Kosmetikstudio <br />Beauty Cosmetics, St. Gallen.<br /> Alle Behandlungen
            werden von mir, Dr. Nicolas Scheffbuch, persönlich durchgeführt.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

